                     <interp inst="t18280911-222-person1275" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am landlord of the Plough - the prisoner came there on the 10th of August, and called for a glass of porter; he then asked me to send this book to W. Smith - I got a man to take it; I had never seen the prisoner before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-222-person1276">
                  FRANCIS 
                  EVANS
